  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 17-17-27, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO REMOVE THE PROHIBITION ON COMMERCIAL HAZARDOUS WASTE AND UNDERGROUND INJECTION WELLS; TO AMEND SECTION 17-17-151, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO REMOVE REFERENCES TO THE MISSISSIPPI CAPACITY ASSURANCE PLAN; TO AMEND SECTION 17-17-153, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO REMOVE CERTAIN REFERENCES TO FEDERAL REQUIREMENTS UNDER THE COMPREHENSIVE ENVIRONMENTAL RESPONSE, COMPENSATION AND LIABILITY ACT OF 1980 FOR STATE CAPACITY ASSURANCE PLANS; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
